{"id":349897,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/06/bbc｜黑龙江安达快餐店爆炸　警方曾接恐吓/","date":"2014-06-08T13:13:36Z","modified":"2014-06-08T13:13:36Z","title":"BBC｜黑龙江安达快餐店爆炸　警方曾接恐吓","content":"<h1 id=\"page-title\" class=\"title\" style=\"color: #000000;\"><img src=\"http://www.botanwang.com/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/field/image/Clipboard01_17.jpg?itok=4I6bDbUt\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"330\" /></h1>\n<div class=\"content-middle\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\n<div class=\"region region-content\">\n<div id=\"block-system-main\" class=\"block block-system\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<form id=\"article-node-form--2\" class=\"node-form node-article-form\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" action=\"http://www.botanwang.com/articles/201406/%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%BE%BE%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E3%80%80%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A5%E6%81%90%E5%90%93.html\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\" method=\"post\">\n<div class=\"panel-flexible panels-flexible-13 clearfix\">\n<div class=\"panel-flexible-inside panels-flexible-13-inside\">\n<div class=\"panels-flexible-row panels-flexible-row-13-main-row panels-flexible-row-first clearfix\">\n<div class=\"inside panels-flexible-row-inside panels-flexible-row-13-main-row-inside panels-flexible-row-inside-first clearfix\">\n<div class=\"panels-flexible-region panels-flexible-region-13-center panels-flexible-region-first panels-flexible-region-last\">\n<div class=\"inside panels-flexible-region-inside panels-flexible-region-13-center-inside panels-flexible-region-inside-first panels-flexible-region-inside-last\">\n<div class=\"panel-pane pane-node-body\">\n<div class=\"pane-content\">\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden\">\n<div class=\"field-items\">\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\n<p>黑龙江绥化安达市一家快餐店发生爆炸物爆炸，造成两名干警受伤。据中国官方媒体报道，警方事前曾接获恐吓。</p>\n<p>新华社引述中共安达市委宣传部说，星期天（6月8日）早上9时34分（格林尼治标准时间1时34分），安达正阳四道街上的德克士快餐店发生了爆炸。</p>\n<p>报道引述绥化市公安局局长盛威说，安达市公安指挥中心此前接报称，附近一家德克士快餐厅将于5分钟左右发生爆炸。警方疏散群众时发生爆炸，造成两名警察受伤。</p>\n<p>中国中央电视台报道，警方已定性为刑事案件，初步怀疑是人为报复。</p>\n<p>从网民上传微博的照片所见，发生爆炸的快餐店发生大火，地面散满玻璃碎片，多辆消防车到场扑救。</p>\n<p>中共《人民日报》网站引述一名目击者称，发生爆炸的位置位于快餐店二楼；广州《南方都市报》微博引述目击者“bakeshame”称，现场传来两声巨响，一、二楼部分玻璃震碎，顾客及服务员纷纷向外跑，约10分钟后浓烟及火苗从二楼窜出。</p>\n<p>此前，中国接连发生暴力袭击，北京当局定性为涉及新疆分离主义分子的“暴力恐怖袭击”，并宣布开展为期一年的全国反恐行动。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n","author":999,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,8779],"tags":[20889,13370]}